âš™ï¸ 3. Tech Stack
Component	Tool
Data Processing	PySpark
Semantic Embeddings	Sentence-Transformers (MiniLM)
Storage	Parquet (local) or FAISS (for similarity)
Interface	Python script or FastAPI endpoint
Hardware	CPU/GPU (optional for faster embedding)

